OL,6,FA man who raped a stranded teenage bus
OL,7,Fpassenger after her phone died will be
OL,8,Fdeported following his 10-year prison
OL,9,Fterm.
OL,11,FChiemka Okoronta, 29, was the only
OL,12,Fother remaining passenger on board the
OL,13,Fbus when the 17-year-old girl was told
OL,14,Fshe would have to get a taxi back to
OL,15,Fher home in Bradford after its final
OL,16,Fstop in Morley, Leeds.
OL,18,FOkoronta, of Morley Street, Bradford,
OL,19,Foffered to share the fare but instead
OL,20,Fdirected the driver back to his flat,
OL,21,Fwhere he attacked her.
