OL,6,FHe was found guilty of three counts of
OL,7,Frape and causing a woman to engage in
OL,8,Fsexual activity and was jailed for 10
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FBradford Crown Court heard he will be
OL,12,Fdeported to his native Nigeria after
OL,13,Fhis release.
OL,15,FThe court was told the incident
OL,16,Fhappened after the girl's bus
OL,17,Fterminated in Leeds on 25 March.
