OL,6,FProsecutor Graham Dowling said: "She
OL,7,Fgot off the bus and attempted to call
OL,8,Fa friend for help but her phone
OL,9,Fbattery had died and she told the
OL,10,Fdefendant, who offered to share a taxi
OL,11,Fwith her.
OL,13,F"She agreed and gave him her remaining
OL,14,Fmoney - #4.90 in cash.
OL,16,F"In the taxi, he chose to sit in the
OL,17,Fback with her and began making kissing
OL,18,Fgestures at her. The defendant has
OL,19,Fbooked the taxi to his home address
OL,20,Fwhen she thought they were going to
OL,21,FBradford bus station."
