OL,6,FHe persuaded the girl to go inside and
OL,7,Fforced her into the toilet, where he
OL,8,Flocked the door and raped her.
OL,10,FAfter the attack, the girl managed to
OL,11,Fstop a passer-by and use their phone
OL,12,Fto call 999.
OL,14,FIn a statement the girl said: "It
OL,15,Fturned my life upside down. Since, I
OL,16,Fhave had multiple flashbacks of that
OL,17,Fnight and nightmares. Every now and
OL,18,Fthen I have to go to the doctors for
OL,19,Fmedication.
