OL,6,F"This was a sustained incident. The
OL,7,Fcomplainant was clearly very
OL,8,Fvulnerable."
OL,10,FFollowing the sentencing, Det Con Sue
OL,11,FSutcliffe, of Bradford District
OL,12,FSafeguarding Unit, said: "I would like
OL,13,Fto commend the victim in this case for
OL,14,Fher immense bravery in coming forward
OL,15,Fstraight away to report this horrific
OL,16,Fcrime.
OL,18,F"I would urge anyone who has been the
OL,19,Fvictim of a sexual offence, to please
OL,20,Freport it to us so we can take action."
